      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Started <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        <a href="https://github.com/arpit2006/CampussCompass.git" target="_blank" class="btn btn-secondary btn-large"><i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i> View GitHub</a>
