        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 18px;">
          Traditional platforms overwhelm you with thousands of elective options, paid certificates, or AI-generated roadmaps that change every time you refresh. 
        </p>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 28px;">
          CampusCompass brings structure back to your semesters. We curate a single, peer-vetted roadmap for each tech career path, helping you ignore the noise and focus on what actually moves the needle during college.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Key Metrics -->
        <div class="why-stats-row">
          <div class="why-stat-item">
            <h4 style="color: var(--primary);">100%</h4>
            <span>Free &amp; Open Source</span>
          </div>
          <div class="why-stat-item">
            <h4 style="color: var(--secondary);">6+</h4>
            <span>Career Tracks</span>
          </div>
          <div class="why-stat-item">
            <h4 style="color: var(--accent);">0</h4>
            <span>No AI Hallucinations</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right: Why Cards Column -->
      <div class="why-cards-col">
        
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon primary">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--text);">Curated by University Seniors</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
              Our paths are designed by seniors and industry professionals who have walked the same path, identifying exactly what libraries and tools to study.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon secondary">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-square-check"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--text);">Zero-Config Progress Matching</h4>
            <p style="font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
              Enter your current skills on your profile page, and your personal timeline dynamically matches and ticks off completed topics automatically.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="why-card">
          <div class="why-card-icon accent">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-play"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
